te><br />\n啲尿屙落個尿兜反彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n要計角道，擦邊咁射入去。<br />\n如果你對到正一正直角咁射落去，肯肯定彈到成褲都係<br />\n記住入射角=出射角呢個概念</blockquote><br />\n對住尿兜左側以同相對左側面較細嘅入射角射落去<br />\n啲尿唔夠逃脫速度 一直黏附喺尿兜<br />\n由左側旋去右側捲落底個窿度唔會反彈<br />\n<br />\n如果向前射就必定彈番自己褲同鞋度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ada85d00bd4bc3e48f7d3174b4e2a331f52c7ec5","tid":176023,"uid":62085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T02:43:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>等陣......點解屙尿會滴到隻腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n啲尿屙落個尿兜反彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n要計角道，擦邊咁射入去。<br />\n如果你對到正一正直角咁射落去，肯肯定彈到成褲都係<br />\n記住入射角=出射角呢個概念</blockquote><br />\n對住尿兜左側以同相對左側面較細嘅入射角射落去<br />\n啲尿唔夠逃脫速度 一直黏附喺尿兜<br />\n由左側旋去右側捲落底個窿度唔會反彈<br />\n<br />\n如果向前射就必定彈番自己褲同鞋度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真係學到野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想問下有冇得調整噴尿速度？唔想激彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c125ae2bccf4181052edfc5e7e97e16cd2d7139","tid":176023,"uid":63253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T05:17:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>等陣......點解屙尿會滴到隻腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n啲尿屙落個尿兜反彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n要計角道，擦邊咁射入去。<br />\n如果你對到正一正直角咁射落去，肯肯定彈到成褲都係<br />\n記住入射角=出射角呢個概念</blockquote><br />\n對住尿兜左側以同相對左側面較細嘅入射角射落去<br />\n啲尿唔夠逃脫速度 一直黏附喺尿兜<br />\n由左側旋去右側捲落底個窿度唔會反彈<br />\n<br />\n如果向前射就必定彈番自己褲同鞋度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真係學到野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想問下有冇得調整噴尿速度？唔想激彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n要忍住放，如果你想享受大力屙果種快感，肯定會彈。<br />\n總知你記住，入射線同反射線型成既角度愈細，就愈彈。角度愈大，愈會沿尿兜向下流。飲多2杯水practice 下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}